<!-----评论列表------>
<template name="commentList_style1">
  <view class="vtu-comment">
    <view class="vtu-comment-user">
      <image src="https://activity.vtuzx.com/doc/vtuui/weapp/avatar/1.png"></image>
    </view>
    <view class="vtu-comment-info">
      <view class="vtu-comment-info-title">
        <view class="vtu-comment-info-title-label">vtu组件</view>
        <view class="vtu-comment-info-title-icon"><i class="iconfont icon-zanshangshouyi"></i> 2</view>
      </view>
      <view class="vtu-comment-info-content">
        <text>真是强大的UI组件，使用简单方便，有丰富的模板组件，功能全面。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="vtu-comment-info-detail">
        <span>1小时前</span>
        <span>回复</span>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</template>
<!-----评论列表------>
<template name="commentList_style2">
  <view class="vtu-comment style2">
    <view class="vtu-comment-user">
      <image src="https://activity.vtuzx.com/doc/vtuui/weapp/avatar/2.png"></image>
    </view>
    <view class="vtu-comment-info">
      <view class="vtu-comment-info-title">
        <view class="vtu-comment-info-title-label font-red">微博样式</view>
      </view>
      <view class="vtu-comment-info-content">
        <text>真是强大的UI组件，使用简单方便，有丰富的模板组件，功能全面。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="vtu-comment-info-reply">
        <view class="vtu-comment-info-reply-li"><span>用户123:</span>很棒，功能很强大，使用也特别简单</view>
        <view class="vtu-comment-info-reply-li"><span>微图知行商城:</span>很厉害</view>
      </view>
      <view class="vtu-comment-info-detail">
        <span>1小时前</span>
        <span class="icon iconfont icon-share"></span>
        <span class="icon iconfont icon-zanshangshouyi"></span>
        <span class="icon iconfont icon-yijian"></span>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</template>
<!-----评论列表------>
<template name="commentList_style3">
  <view class="vtu-comment style3">
    <view class="vtu-comment-top">
      <view class="vtu-comment-user">
        <image src="https://activity.vtuzx.com/doc/vtuui/weapp/avatar/3.png"></image>
      </view>
      <view class="vtu-comment-top-label font-orange">匿名买家</view>
    </view>
    <view class="vtu-comment-info-detail">
      <span>2019-07-09</span>
      <span>颜色分类:白色</span>
      <span>尺码:M</span>
    </view>
    <view class="vtu-comment-info-content">
      <text>真是强大的UI组件，使用简单方便，有丰富的模板组件，功能全面。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="vtu-comment-img">
      <view class="vtu-comment-img-li" wx:for="{{imgList}}" wx:for-item="img"><image src="{{img}}" mode="aspectFill"></image></view>
    </view>
    <view class="vtu-comment-info-detail">
      <span>233次浏览</span>
      <span class="icon iconfont icon-share"><font>分享</font></span>
      <span class="icon iconfont icon-zanshangshouyi"><font>点赞</font></span>
      <span class="icon iconfont icon-yijian"><font>评论</font></span>
    </view>
  </view>
</template>


<!-----聊天列表------>
<template name="chatList_style1">
  <view class="vtu-chat">
    <view class="vtu-chat-user">
      <image src="{{src}}"></image>
    </view>
    <view class="vtu-chat-info">
      <view class="vtu-chat-info-top">
        <view class="vtu-chat-info-top-name">施瓦辛格</view>
        <view class="vtu-chat-info-top-time">3小时前</view>
      </view>
      <view class="vtu-chat-info-content">
        <view class="vtu-chat-info-content-detail">很高兴认识你</view>
        <view class="vtu-chat-info-content-icon"></view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</template>

